58368729822491100", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1498170157176393731/tyrdhQ1M_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Alec Stapp", "username": "AlecStapp"}, "content": "The US tech industry would be a shadow of itself without immigrants.\n\nFirst 10 examples that come to mind:\n\n1. Elon Musk (South Africa)\n\n2. Andrej Karpathy (Czechoslovakia)\n\n3. Sergey Brin (Russia)\n\n4. Jensen Huang (Taiwan)\n\n5. Satya Nadella (India)\n\n6. Ilya Sutskever (Russia)", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 1193}, "images": [{"width": 1260, "heightRatio": 117, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HJGG8nHWwAAmFlD.jpg", "height": 1482}, {"width": 1260, "heightRatio": 117, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HJGG8nHWgAADZU2.jpg", "height": 1475}, {"width": 1259, "heightRatio": 116, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HJGG8nGWQAE-5Mu.jpg", "height": 1473}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 0, "created": 1779637473000, "id": "2058574883626308093", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1498170157176393731/tyrdhQ1M_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Alec Stapp", "username": "AlecStapp"}, "content": "People in the replies pushing back that \u201cSatya Nadella, Sundar Pichai & Sanjay Mehrotra didn\u2019t found their companies.\u201d\n\nTrue\u2026 they\u2019ve all only just >10x\u2019d the value the their companies since taking over as CEO.\n\nCreating massive wealth & prosperity for Americans in the process.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 959}, "likes": 0}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsZF0ZAf", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 89, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8638881, "raw_content": "", "author": "okaythennews", "created": 1779713920315, "profile_picture": "Wuq5lB0NPQre", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_auth